    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in impeccable mechanical health. This example features the S54B32 inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS to achieve its 8,000 RPM redline. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including VAC coated rod bearings and a reinforced rear subframe with Turner plates. The 6-speed Getrag manual provides precise engagement, delivering power through a limited-slip differential. The suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein B16 coilovers, maintaining factory geometry while enhancing lateral grip. Finished in Carbon Black with flawless paint depth and a pristine Cinnamon Nappa leather interior, this chassis is free of typical E46 fatigue. A turn-key powerhouse for the purist.",
